title: VIDEO: This Shadowhunters First Look of Clary Meeting Jace Is Everything
text: VIDEO: This Shadowhunters First Look of Clary Meeting Jace Is Everything Saturday, 10 October 2015 (11 minutes ago) ABC Family has released the first look at its highly anticipated new series Shadowhunters, premiering on Tuesday, Jan 12 at 9/8c. On Shadowhunters, based on Cassandra Clare's Mortal Instruments books, Clary Fray learns that she comes from a line of Shadowhunters, human-angel hybrids who hunt demons.
